sentences.chinese: 老百姓都称其为“骨架电话机”。

sentences.english: OBJECTIVE To prepare the helicid hydrophile matrix tablet.

sentences.english: We design the backbone of the application -- the architecture.
sentences.chinese: 我们设计应用程序的骨架，即架构。

sentences.english: Now their skeleton forever has kept on museum Chen Liejia.
sentences.chinese: 现在它们的骨架永远地留在了博物馆的陈列架上。

sentences.english: The stub and skeleton objects also take care of beginning and committing container-managed transactions.
sentences.chinese: 存根和骨架对象还负责开始和提交容器管理的事务。

sentences.english: The microfilament in the microvilli and pseudopodia is the motion skeleton of cancer cells.
sentences.chinese: 微绒毛及伪足内的微丝是瘤细胞的运动骨架。

sentences.english: The process of connecting the skeleton to the mesh is known as skinning.
sentences.chinese: 这个链接骨架和网格的过程就是蒙皮。

sentences.english: Both microtubule and actin cytoskeleton have been shown to be involved in proper nuclear positioning.
sentences.chinese: 细胞骨架微管和肌动蛋白都参与了细胞核定位的过程。

sentences.english: About every seven years, your body replaces the equivalent of an entirely new skeleton.
sentences.chinese: 每七年，你的身体就会有一个完整的新骨架生长出来。

sentences.english: Objective To study the influential factors of the release rate of neogambogic acid from sustained release matrix tablets.
sentences.chinese: 目的研究新藤黄酸骨架片体外释药速率的影响因素。

sentences.english: The chicken carcass can be rendered down to make stock.
sentences.chinese: 鸡的骨架可以熬成鸡汤。

sentences.english: The block is still just a skeleton of girders.

sentences.english: The main bridge of the Tiangong Bridge is a steel-frame reinforced concrete arch bridge.
sentences.chinese: 天工大桥主桥为一座劲性骨架钢筋混凝土拱桥。

sentences.english: METHODS Wet granulation technique was employed to prepare pectin-calcium chloride matrix tablets.
sentences.chinese: 方法湿法制粒压片法制备吲哚美辛果胶氯化钙骨架片。

sentences.english: The reduced density of the bird skeleton provided a light but strong frame.
sentences.chinese: 减轻了的骨架密度则提供了轻巧而坚固的身体框架。

sentences.english: The architectural skeleton is then incrementally fleshed out with details.
sentences.chinese: 然后，逐步用细节充实体系结构骨架。
